model
Class Piece

java.lang.Object
  model.Piece

public class Piece
extends java.lang.Object

The Piece class is a mutable class. The Piece class represents the different types of chess pieces that exist in the Antichess game. Each piece has a PieceType, and also a color associated with it. Also, each piece retains the knowledge of whether or not it is has been moved since the game started.

Specification Fields
  • isWhite : boolean //boolean representing if the Piece is white
  • hasMoved : boolean //boolean representing if the Piece has moved yet
  • type : PieceType //the type of chess piece this Piece represents
